53
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:09,280
Put the vernacular poem further back.

54
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,200
This article "A Preliminary Discussion of Language Reform" is more influential.

55
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,080
Wait, why has it changed to "Reform?"

56
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,440
Isn't it a revolution?

57
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,120
This carries a lot less weight.

58
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,400
Is this kid scared?

59
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,560
It's understandable that young people have their worries.

60
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,760
If he wants "Reform" so be it.

61
