If no one in Beijing shows up to support "New Youth",

83
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,840
does it have any influence?

84
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,200
I think this can not be delayed.

85
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,188
Next week, next week we will leave.

86
00:03:09,468 --> 00:03:10,039
Next week?

87
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,906
Next week.

88
