420
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,200
Where is he living? Do you know?

421
00:18:43,360 --> 00:18:44,160
I will ask around.

422
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:46,640
Yes. Please.

423
00:18:48,080 --> 00:18:50,080
Zhongfu, listen to me. Zhongfu.

