473
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:02,080
Even now, I often see it in my dreams.

474
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:05,120
True, true.

475
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:08,000
At the time, if you hadn't given that shove...

476
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:10,640
I would not be sitting in front of you today.

477
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:12,640
Dead as a doornail, long ago.

478
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,400
Brother Zhongfu,

479
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,640
you saved my life.

480
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,480
I have to properly thank you.

481
00:22:18,560 --> 00:22:20,160
You're too kind. You're overstating it.

482
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:22,960
Twelve years ago,

483
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:25,360
I was the age you are now.

484
00:22:26,400 --> 00:22:27,440
At that time,

485
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:29,840
there was nothing I was afraid of doing, nothing I was afraid of saying. 

486
00:22:30,080 --> 00:22:31,520
I was brave and unyielding.

487
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,360
But now I am old.

488
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,360
No longer have that edge.

489
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:38,640
And not as driven as times gone by.

490
00:22:39,680 --> 00:22:41,440
You're not doing so bad.

491
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:43,200
Nowadays, you, Chen Duxiu,

492
00:22:43,440 --> 00:22:45,680
