495
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,360
A breath of fresh air.

496
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:56,560
I read every issue of your magazine "New Youth."

497
00:22:56,600 --> 00:22:58,480
With each reading, there's always something to be gained.

498
00:22:58,640 --> 00:23:00,560
Sir, if you would like to submit a manuscript,

499
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:02,400
I would be extremely grateful.

500
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:06,240
That is a matter of course. Naturally I will contribute.

501
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:10,400
I came here today

502
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:15,120
