506
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:30,480
Take a look. Letter of appointment.

507
00:23:38,560 --> 00:23:40,000
Congratulations, sir.

508
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:48,960
I would like you to come to Peking University to be the Dean of Liberal Arts.

509
00:23:49,840 --> 00:23:51,280
Lend me a hand.

510
00:23:51,760 --> 00:23:53,360
Lend Peking University a hand.

511
00:23:53,840 --> 00:23:56,880
I hope Brother Zhongfu would not decline.

512
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,320
I would like to thank Brother Jiemin for the support.

513
00:24:06,640 --> 00:24:08,080
