517
00:24:17,040 --> 00:24:20,080
leading the various disciplines of the humanities and social science.

518
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:23,840
Aren't you currently advocating and calling for

519
00:24:24,080 --> 00:24:25,440
democratic science?

520
00:24:26,240 --> 00:24:30,400
I think this would be your best stage to do so.

521
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:34,880
Precisely because it's a serious responsibility,

522
00:24:35,120 --> 00:24:37,440
I don't want to rashly accept an appointment.

523
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:41,120
After all, I haven't properly gone to university.

524
00:24:41,520 --> 00:24:44,000
And have no experience teaching or educating others.

525
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,680
An incompetent person who pretends to be competent

526
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,360
will only hinder the progress of their students.

527
00:24:47,600 --> 00:24:50,320
If I actually got in the way of your grand undertaking,

528
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:52,480
there would be no greater crime.

529
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:56,240
Don't decline in such a rush.

530
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:59,360
It's true that this is very abrupt.

531
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:02,000
You can discuss this at your leisure

532
00:25:02,240 --> 00:25:04,320
with friends and family and then make a decision.

533
00:25:04,800 --> 00:25:08,720
I am indeed eager in my search for talent.

534
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:11,040
I am determined to invite you

535
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:13,520
to Peking University and work together.

536
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:17,200
For China. For education in China.

537
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:22,560
For Master Cai to show such high regard for me,

538
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:24,480
I am truly moved to tears.

539
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:27,280
If Peking University is to become China's highest educational institution,

540
00:25:27,760 --> 00:25:30,240
it will be the best platform to advocate for science and democracy.

541
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:32,880
If there is an opportunity to follow Brother Jiemin

542
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,840
to Peking University and collaborate on this endeavour,

543
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:39,400
it would be the blessing of three lifetimes, exactly what I've been looking for.

544
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,160
But to be quite honest,

545
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:42,960
in my heart,

546
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:45,280
I can't let go of my "New Youth."

547
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:48,960
This magazine is still a fledgling

548
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:51,040
that has just started picking up.

549
00:25:51,360 --> 00:25:52,400
I came to Beijing this time

550
00:25:52,640 --> 00:25:55,040
precisely because of the magazine. Looking for investors and resources.

551
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:57,040
A successful harvest.

552
00:25:57,280 --> 00:25:58,880
Only just today, I've discussed

553
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:01,600
an investment of over a hundred thousand shares.

554
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:04,560
At a time like this,

555
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:06,400
if I leave "New Youth" behind without a care

556
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:08,000
to take a position at Peking University,

557
00:26:08,160 --> 00:26:09,520
wouldn't I be letting down

558
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,600
everyone's deep regard?

559
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:14,800
It's true. I understand.

560
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:18,960
What you are saying is not without reason.

561
00:26:19,440 --> 00:26:21,680
If the result of you coming to Peking University

562
00:26:22,480 --> 00:26:24,800
is the stoppage of the publication of "New Youth."

563
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:29,520
That's unacceptable.

564
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:35,360
Alright. I will now hurry back

565
00:26:36,080 --> 00:26:38,720
to discuss how to solve the problem of "New Youth."

566
00:26:39,280 --> 00:26:41,280
Zhongfu, my thinking is this.

567
00:26:41,840 --> 00:26:44,560
Peking University must exist. "New Youth" must keep running.

568
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:47,680
I will definitely find a way to satisfy both requirements.

569
00:26:48,240 --> 00:26:49,440
Alright. I'm leaving.

570
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:53,200
Brother Jiemin.

571
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,640
Brother Zhongfu.

572
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:58,960
Let's just call today my first of three humble visits to plead my case.

573
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:02,160
Ok. I will get going.

574
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:19,520
Brother Mengzou,

575
00:27:19,760 --> 00:27:22,080
I beg of you to handle the matter of signing the contracts.

576
00:27:22,320 --> 00:27:24,240
I have nothing to say to those business men.

577
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:26,080
I would only get in the way.

578
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,320
What? What do you mean?

579
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:32,080
You're not going?

580
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:35,200
Zhongfu, everyone is coming to see you.

581
00:27:35,440 --> 00:27:36,720
Signing the contract is such an important thing.

582
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,960
If you don't show up, how will I explain it to them?

583
00:27:40,080 --> 00:27:42,080
Just say I have an important meeting.

584
00:27:42,400 --> 00:27:43,360
And it's the truth.

585
00:27:43,600 --> 00:27:45,760
I need to go to Taoran Pavilion to see Quan Xuantong.

586
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:50,400
You're a really strange person.

587
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,920
It's snowing so hard.

588
00:27:52,160 --> 00:27:53,040
And it's so cold.

589
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:55,120
What are you doing meeting someone at Taoran Pavilion?

590
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:56,720
To sample the northwesterly wind?

591
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:58,320
You don't understand.

592
00:27:58,560 --> 00:28:00,000
Heavy snow is romantic.

593
00:28:00,560 --> 00:28:02,960
This is the difference between a reader of books and a seller of books.

594
00:28:03,200 --> 00:28:05,440
To make joy amidst misery is the essence of a scholar.

595
00:28:08,320 --> 00:28:11,920
Not many people these days can keep in tune with such highbrow sentiments.

596
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,480
I surmise

597
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:16,720
Master Qian will not be singing the same tune.

598
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:18,080
And I surmise

599
00:28:18,320 --> 00:28:20,720
at this very moment Qian Xuantong is already on his way there.

600
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:23,600
Zhongfu. Zhongfu.

601
00:28:23,840 --> 00:28:25,280
Don't, Zhongfu.

602
00:28:25,840 --> 00:28:27,920
No, if you leave, what do I do?

603
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:39,520
Brother Zhongfu!

604
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,440
Deqian, is that you?

605
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:43,960
I've been looking forward to meeting you. Your reputation preceeds you. 

606
00:28:44,080 --> 00:28:46,240
Today, I finally see your face in person.

607
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:50,480
Myriad entities have different forms, but they are the same in essence.

608
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,720
Though in the corners of the world, we have never met,

609
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,240
we have long since been alike in spirit.

610
00:28:54,480 --> 00:28:55,120
This is true.

611
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:56,640
I am a faithful reader of "New Youth"
[Qian Xuantong, styled Deqian: Peking University professor]

612
00:28:56,880 --> 00:28:59,200
and a die-hard supporter of you, Chen Duxiu.

613
00:28:59,600 --> 00:29:01,440
Deqian, you are too modest.

614
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:02,160
How is it?

615
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:04,640
To meet at Taoran pavilion in the snow today.

616
00:29:04,880 --> 00:29:05,840
You don't find it odd?

617
00:29:06,080 --> 00:29:07,040
To see Taoran in the snow?

618
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:08,240
'Elegant' is the only word for it.

619
00:29:08,480 --> 00:29:09,280
How can it be odd?

620
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,560
You don't find it cold?

621
00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:14,640
To meet brother Zhongfu is to be bathed in spring wind. 

622
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,240
Any chill is entirely absent.

623
00:29:16,560 --> 00:29:18,000
We are indeed fellow travellers.

624
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,440
We have another fellow traveller.

625
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:20,400
Let me introduce you.

626
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:21,920
This is Liu Bannong.

627
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:22,960
Literary translator.

628
00:29:23,200 --> 00:29:25,840
and famed writer of the "Mandarin Ducks and Butterflies" school of fiction.

629
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,440
Bannong,

630
00:29:27,680 --> 00:29:29,840
I've read many of your translations of European fiction.

631
00:29:30,080 --> 00:29:31,580
It has benefited me a great deal.

632
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:33,040
Compared to you, sir,

633
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:35,520
I am but a handful of soil next to Mount Tai.

634
00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:37,440
Why are the people in Beijing

635
00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:39,040
all so modest?

636
00:29:40,160 --> 00:29:41,440
Brother Zhongfu, let's talk in the pavilion.

637
00:29:41,520 --> 00:29:42,400
Certainly.

638
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:44,240
Speaking of Taoran Pavilion,

639
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,380
among the most famous of its associations

640
00:29:45,520 --> 00:29:47,440
is the composition by Jiang Zao, "Taoran Pavilion."

641
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,440
Reportedly, he often invited

642
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:51,360
scholars and literati, colleagues and close friends

643
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,040
to come here to feast and compose poetry.

